"GL2422AP-6T3-B10 VER T1.2" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The DWL-800AP can function as a stand-alone access point or also as a repeater. With a [http://www.seattlewireless.net/dwl800ap%2Bhack slight firmware modification] the device can also serve as a wireless bridge (DWL-810+).
